  <brief_title>Study Evaluating The Safety Of Subcutaneous Methylnaltrexone In Treatment Of Opioid-Induced Constipation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open-Label Extension Study To Assess The Safety Of A Fixed Dose Of Subcutaneous Methylnaltrexone In Subjects With Advanced Illness And Opioid-Induced Constipation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Valeant Pharmaceuticals International, Inc.</agency>
